title: Instruments of Death   (History Channel  2012  -  Complete)
description:
Each episode of Instruments of Death looks at how these weapons took out specific targets, explores the effects of blades and bullets on a human body and reveals how battlefield wounds were treated by surgeons on the frontlines.

Episode 1: The English Civil War
The Battle of Naseby 1645

Episode 2: The Wars Of The Roses
The Battle Of Towton 1461

Episode 3: The Norman Invasion
The Battle of Hastings 1066

Episode 4: The Great War - The Battle of the Somme 1916

Episode 5: The Wars of the Roses: The Battle of Towton 1461

Episode 6: The Napoleonic Wars: The Battle of Waterloo 1815



Enjoy and Seed!!
